k":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-Tc","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":22796,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/30\/sin-disturb-conscience-heart-fatwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":3422,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Conscience: Sin shakes your heart, even if scholars approve","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tha\u2019laba reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me what is lawful and unlawful for me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRighteousness is serenity in the soul and peace of mind in the heart. Sin is not serene in the soul and not satisfying\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38371,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/hajj-purifies-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":3422,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Pilgrimage purifies from sins and poverty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform the Hajj and \u2018Umrah pilgrimages, one after another, for they both erase poverty and sins just as the furnace removes impurity from iron, gold, and silver. There is no reward for an accepted Hajj\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11828,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/iman-leave-sins-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":3422,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Conscience: Leave sins that shake your soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: A man asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhat is faith?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf you are happy with your good deeds and saddened by your bad deeds, you are a believer.\u201d The man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is sin?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/10\/purpose-learning-taqwa-righteousness\/","url_meta":{"origin":3422,"position":3},"title":"Sufyan on Knowledge: Purpose of learning is to be God-fearing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cSurely, sacred knowledge is only studied to become mindful of Allah. Knowledge is only favored over other virtues because it makes one fearful of Allah.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u02bb Baya\u0304n al-\u02bbIlm li-Ibn 'Abd al-Barr 1159 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-purification-heart\/","url_meta":{"o